content:
The new industriesDigitalLending namespace has these new classes.

New Classes
In the Digital Lending application intake process, invoke utility methods from OmniScripts
Use the DigitalLendingIntakeRecordsWrapper class.
In the Digital Lending post intake within FlexCards, invoke utility methods from integration procedures
Use the DigitalLendingUtils class.
Use the DigitalLendingPostIntakeRecordsWrapper class.
In the Digital Lending FlexCards, invoke utility methods from integration procedures
Use the DigitalLendingProductsApi class.
Use the PricingExecutionWrapper class.
title: New Apex Namespace in Digital Lending
